"index_reference": "5938",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Heaviness of heart brought about through disappointment, disillusionment, failure or sin. It can lead to depression of spirit, but this can be relieved.</p>\n<h2>Sadness caused by disappointment or disillusionment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:1-Neh2:3\">NEH 2:1–2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:6-Gen40:7\">GEN 40:6–40:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:4\">1KI 21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl6:1-Eccl6:2\">ECC 6:1–6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:1-Isa19:10\">ISA 19:1–19:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21-Matt19:22\">MAT 19:21–19:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21-Mark10:22\">MRK 10:21–10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22-Luke18:23\">LUK 18:22–18:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:21-Matt26:22\">MAT 26:21–26:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:17\">LUK 24:17</a></p>\n<h2>Sadness leading to depression of spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:14-Num11:15\">NUM 11:14–11:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:7\">JOS 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:3-1Kgs19:4\">1KI 19:3–19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:3-Ps42:4\">PSA 42:3–42:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:10\">JER 15:10</a></p>\n<h2>The relief of sadness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:5-Ps42:6\">PSA 42:5–42:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:25\">PRO 12:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:30\">PRO 15:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:22\">PRO 17:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:6-Prov31:7\">PRO 31:6–31:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:19\">PHP 2:19</a></p>",
